Package edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.ling.extract

Defines the abstract process of XML markup extraction by chunk processors

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IChunkProcessor
    IChunkProcessor processes a chunk in a processing context
    IChunkProcessorProvider
    IChunkProcessorProvider provides its clients with IChunkProcessors
    IFirstChunkProcessor
    An IFirstChunkProcessor is used for the first chunk appearing in a sentence
    ILastChunkProcessor
    ILastChunkProcessor is used for the last chunk appearing in a sentence
